        <h3>Growing a Greener Future: Tree Plantation Initiative at Draktsho</h3>
        <p>Sherubtse GNH Unit in collaboration with G17 UAC Sherubtse SDG 15, organized a tree plantation at Draktsho Vocational Training Centre on 22nd March 2025 in an effort to promote environmental sustainability.As part of the initiative, 27 saplings were planted around the center campus, reinforcing a commitment to a greener environment. The event aimed to enhance greenery at Draktsho while also fostering a sense of community engagement and responsibility toward nature.
        </p>
