        <p>In a significant step towards ensuring clean and safe water for the community, volunteers from Sherubtse College successfully cleaned four major water tanks on 22 March 2025.
          The initiative was organized collaboratively by the Mathematical Sciences Forum, the Social Service Unit (SSU), and the Rovers Unit to commemorate World Water Day.
          </p>
